@startuml
autonumber

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam maxMessageSize 400

actor "Admin Sistem" as Admin
boundary "UI Keuangan" as UI
control "Finance Controller" as Controller
database "DB" as DB

== 1. Pengelolaan Pengeluaran ==
Admin -> UI : Masukkan biaya (Operasional / Pajak)
UI -> Controller : Simpan data biaya operasional
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Simpan rincian biaya operasional & konfigurasi pajak
Controller -> DB : Sinkronisasi pengeluaran periode berjalan
Controller --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil (Data ter-update)
deactivate Controller

== 2. Laporan Performa (Omset & Laba) ==
Admin -> UI : Pilih Periode Laporan
UI -> Controller : Ambil data laporan performa
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Kumpulkan data pendapatan & pengeluaran
DB --> Controller : Data Transaksi
Controller -> Controller : Hitung Laba Kotor & Laba Bersih
Controller --> UI : Tampilkan visualisasi grafik & ringkasan laba
deactivate Controller
@enduml